commit.message:
"United States" -> "United States of America"

Changed on 2014-12-18 as part of the general alignment of ISO-3166 with UNTERM.
Bump version to 0.8 and add setup.cfg

Update short name for CZ and GB

- Czech Republic -> Czechia
- United Kingdom -> United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland

The ISO short name for the United Kingdom was aligned with UNTERM back
in December 2014.

Add new "apolitical_name" field

The apolitical_name field is intended to provide a less inflammatory
phrasing in cases where the ISO-3166 name is particularly controversial.

This feature is initially intended to address Taiwan and Palestine, but
it may be expanded in the future.
